    <main>
        <section class="intro">
            <h2>Welcome to GovtPath!</h2>
            <p>At GovtPath, we are dedicated to transforming the way you connect with job opportunities. Our mission is simple: to bridge the gap between job seekers and employers, making the hiring process smoother, faster, and more efficient.</p>
            <img src="https://img.freepik.com/free-photo/rag-doll-lined-up-one-red-through-magnifying-glass_1156-638.jpg?t=st=1726467796~exp=1726471396~hmac=3330ab83ba72d67bd8d2f3fd7c6819cfcdf7e06e79584301bc8c01d0c5e0e4ad&w=740" alt="Welcome to GovtPath">
